Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.57,0:00:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did Kyousuke say that?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.11,0:00:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lead the Little Busters from now on.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.50,0:00:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,From this moment on, Riki,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.86,0:00:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you are the leader of the Little Busters!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.73,0:00:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm{\i0} the leader?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.83,0:00:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to be another one of his jokes.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.68,0:00:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just screwing with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.02,0:00:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.93,0:00:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The Little Busters are the best!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.06,0:00:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for baseball!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.48,0:00:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so pumped up!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.55,0:00:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.09,0:01:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.62,0:01:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's with that jacket?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.75,0:01:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I made this Little Busters jacket myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.64,0:01:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.59,0:01:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You made it yourself?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.64,0:01:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the embroidery?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.34,0:01:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Creepy.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.45,0:01:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You made this logo yourself too?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.05,0:01:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.90,0:01:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It took me all night.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.10,0:01:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.20,0:01:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what to think.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.85,0:01:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm honestly feeling really happy right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.98,0:01:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.23,0:01:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for some baseball! Time for morning practice!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.01,0:01:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Kengo's turned into an idiot.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.53,0:01:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.28,0:01:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A screw must've come loose when he jumped off the roof!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.59,0:01:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably always had the potential to be like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.75,0:01:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think he'd go straight to top gear though.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.00,0:01:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.81,0:01:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.63,0:02:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll head over with the Little Busters March I thought up!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.93,0:02:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, Little Busters!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.02,0:02:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great for muscles too!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.01,0:02:09.02,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{Kengo}Three, four, Little Busters!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.35,0:02:12.62,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{Muscleheads}One, two, Little Busters!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.79,0:02:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,At long last, Kengo has joined us.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.61,0:02:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing baseball with these members...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.57,0:02:16.98,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{Muscleheads}Three, four, Little Busters!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.31,0:02:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like we're kids again.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.78,0:02:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And everyone else is here too.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.88,0:02:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Game time!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.39,0:02:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're winning this!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.15,0:02:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafu!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.83,0:02:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is our first game!
