Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.72,0:02:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{CM}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.41,0:02:51.24,Top,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.24,0:02:53.96,Top,,0,0,0,,Let's do some final touch-ups before our first game.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.96,0:02:55.65,Top,,0,0,0,,What are we going to practice, Riki?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.48,0:02:58.38,Top,,0,0,0,,You're in charge, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.38,0:02:59.94,Top,,0,0,0,,I am?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.94,0:03:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.28,0:03:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the leader anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.53,0:03:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious, Kyousuke?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.78,0:03:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a third-year.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.14,0:03:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about time I drew the line.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.33,0:03:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of leaving everything to you from here on.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.92,0:03:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, this is way too sudden!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.20,0:03:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about it for a while now.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.42,0:03:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since we decided to start playing baseball,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.69,0:03:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought of some day making you the leader.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think everyone would agree—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:28.18,Top,,0,0,0,,Riki!                           Riki!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.18,0:03:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ri-Ri-Ri-Ri-Riki-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.90,0:03:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki-kun! Riki-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.82,0:03:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Fan, fan, fan.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.19,0:03:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes sense. Kyousuke's got job searching to do, anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.50,0:03:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kind of unreliable, but you'd make an okay leader!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.24,0:03:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on being the new leader!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.98,0:03:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.79,0:03:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry too much about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.04,0:03:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just try giving it a shot.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows, you might even be good at it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.39,0:03:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.18,0:04:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're undoubtedly much weaker than Kyousuke-san,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.47,0:04:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's also a moe point.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.28,0:04:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no objections as your manager.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.18,0:04:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so what should we practice first?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.05,0:04:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we do a roll call?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.36,0:04:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A roll call?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.06,0:04:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that thing where you call out people's names and they count.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.84,0:04:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It would raise our morale.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll try it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.17,0:04:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyousuke!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.35,0:04:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.67,0:04:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Komari-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.58,0:04:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.41,0:04:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurugaya-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.58,0:04:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Saigusa-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.54,0:04:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.33,0:04:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.26,0:04:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafu!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.29,0:04:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.36,0:04:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see I'm here?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.25,0:04:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishizono-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.62,0:04:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that would be me.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Masato...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.42,0:04:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Riki!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.58,0:04:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to shout my number like I'm supposed to,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.00,0:04:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't know what number I am!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.49,0:04:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't either.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.76,0:04:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki, what about me?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.64,0:04:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.58,0:04:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kengo!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.31,0:04:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.11,0:05:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... perfect.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.64,0:05:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All's well that ends well.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.15,0:05:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It would've been better not to do it...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.54,0:05:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway, how about we all do some fielding practice?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.32,0:05:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what I wanted!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.41,0:05:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,First order!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.50,0:05:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.94,0:05:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{timer: include the "anatatachi"}Wait right there!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.55,0:05:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not allowed on the field today.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.72,0:05:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They're doing maintenance on it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.48,0:05:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The school said they had already told Naoe-kun about it, seeing how his name was on the request form...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.66,0:05:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.25,0:05:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's off...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.82,0:05:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like your first order immediately ended in failure.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.31,0:05:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad about that. Let's do individual training!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.24,0:05:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Practice swings! That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.40,0:05:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How about some snacks?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.16,0:05:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Snacks? Wafu!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.13,0:05:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget about the batting order and fielding positions for the game, as well as the strategy.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to seeing them.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You look nothing like an actual leader.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.63,0:06:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm{\i0} the leader?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.40,0:06:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Batting order, fielding positions, strategy...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.44,0:06:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Where on Earth do I even start?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.01,0:06:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.01,0:06:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kyousuke—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.87,0:06:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.96,0:06:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happened, I would always rely on Kyousuke.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.68,0:06:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been forever...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.05,0:06:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since then...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.33,0:06:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Back when I had lost my parents and was all alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.95,0:07:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was diagnosed with narcolepsy and was afraid of falling asleep at any second.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.03,0:07:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite my condition, Kyousuke took me into a world of fun and laughter.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.47,0:07:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyousuke's back protected me.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.39,0:07:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There was always something fun waiting for me when I followed Kyousuke.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.64,0:07:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play baseball.{ep1}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.69,0:07:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll call ourselves...{ep1}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.04,0:07:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"Little Busters"!{ep1}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.69,0:07:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave me courage.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.10,0:07:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If the world is full of things we never wanted to know,{ep6}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.00,0:07:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is our only option to look the other way?{ep6}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.98,0:07:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,To run away?{ep6}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.41,0:07:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't solve anything by running away.{ep6}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyousuke!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.81,0:08:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking back.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.23,0:08:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I was always so small and worried.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.06,0:08:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I was with you,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.88,0:08:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,all my worries and sadness would just disappear.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.85,0:08:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no different now.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.54,0:08:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're having so much fun because you wanted to play baseball.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.31,0:08:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can think of no other leader but you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.77,0:08:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to keep following you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.57,0:08:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't always rely on me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.51,0:08:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki, you're not as small as you think.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.79,0:08:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're simply unaware of the scale of the things that you've done.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.89,0:08:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.85,0:08:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You've worried for others as much as they did.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.75,0:08:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You helped them overcome their hardship and saved them.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.37,0:08:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It was something only you could do.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.97,0:09:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Little Busters consist of people that {\i1}you{\i0} gathered.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.33,0:09:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not as amazing as you make me out to be.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.85,0:09:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't follow me forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.13,0:09:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to surpass me, Riki.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.25,0:09:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:22.75,brush,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\frx10\c&H13262A&\blur1.2\pos(652,614)}Baseball Team
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.37,0:09:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No no no...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:51.48,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.2\fnJenkins v2.0\c&H8F9495&\blur1\pos(528,248)\frz10.98}Komari-san
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:51.48,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.5\fnJenkins v2.0\c&H8F9495&\blur1.1\pos(774,242)\frz359.3}moodmaker
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:51.48,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.5\fs40\fnJenkins v2.0\c&H8F9495&\blur1\frz359.3\pos(900,298)}it's over if she messes up!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.09,0:09:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Surpassing Kyousuke...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.25,0:09:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That never even occurred to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.57,0:10:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.23,0:10:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Saigusa-san?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.21,0:10:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I scare you?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.62,0:10:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hiding in here.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.33,0:10:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured it'd make you smile.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.41,0:10:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you seem to be worried about something.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.77,0:10:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I just don't think I can replace Kyousuke.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.87,0:10:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the type that can lead a bunch of people.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.41,0:10:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can think of something to make everyone happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.74,0:11:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, if you weren't around,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.80,0:11:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I would probably still think the world was full of hate.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.15,0:11:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've been crushed by my own hate.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.79,0:11:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But because you faced my trouble with everything you had...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.63,0:11:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I watched you make everyone happy...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.71,0:11:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can believe now.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.91,0:11:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That if people think about each other,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.14,0:11:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the world can be filled with light.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.41,0:11:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Riki-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.09,0:11:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru-chin will always be rooting for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.61,0:11:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Saigusa-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.03,0:11:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Mio-chin!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.32,0:11:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you finished with it?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.17,0:11:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've collected some data.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:56.40,Top,,0,0,0,,Sure Win Databook
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.85,0:12:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked into each member of the all-star team
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.08,0:12:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and noted their habits and how to deal with them.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.82,0:12:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use this to think up a strategy against them.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.42,0:12:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You looked this much into it?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.42,0:12:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only normal for a manager.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.55,0:12:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is way more than normal!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.97,0:12:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was always searching for a way to be of use to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.95,0:12:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I was a child, no one could remember me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.36,0:12:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just a pebble on the side of the road.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.93,0:12:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had never called out to me,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.77,0:12:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have been alone forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.81,0:12:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have wished for everyone to forget about me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.19,0:12:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, I'm living a satisfying life with everyone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.78,0:12:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful that I was born.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.27,0:12:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never imagined feeling like this before.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.87,0:12:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You gave me a miracle, Naoe-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.45,0:13:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I only thought about doing for you what Kyousuke had done for me, Nishizono-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.03,0:13:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyousuke is the reason I was able to do anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.55,0:13:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a great leader, Naoe-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.71,0:13:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.03,0:13:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.40,0:14:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki-kun,{Match to TS}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.66,0:14:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,congratulations on becoming leader.{Match to TS}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.38,0:14:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's an invitation to a snack time to celebrate!{Match to TS}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.96,0:14:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,At the place closest to the sky!{Match to TS}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.93,0:14:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The place closest to the sky, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.33,0:14:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, Riki-kun, you're already here!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.51,0:14:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuu-chan and Yui-chan are getting some tea right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.03,0:14:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on up!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.86,0:14:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.99,0:14:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I saw the sky from up here.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.99,0:14:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.07,0:14:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I'll never forget...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.99,0:15:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This was where you taught me not to run away from sad and painful things.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.87,0:15:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And that we can keep smiling when we're with everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.19,0:15:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Komari-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.43,0:15:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, here's the picture book you drew for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.38,0:15:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that I'd have to draw the rest of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.49,0:15:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I did.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.87,0:15:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Little Busters!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.67,0:15:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When one of them smiles, everyone smiles.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.83,0:15:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When one is happy, everyone is happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.40,0:15:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is in a happy, sunny place.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.69,0:15:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And that place is sunny because of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.48,0:15:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.91,0:15:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you gathered us all together.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.13,0:15:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.14,0:15:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And you were the one who told me that I should just be myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.54,0:15:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So now it's my turn to say...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.53,0:15:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You should just be yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.22,0:15:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I should just be myself?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.97,0:16:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You've helped us all already, so now it's our turn to support you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.05,0:16:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the type of kind leader you are.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.18,0:16:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.02,0:16:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Your kindness is your strength.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.15,0:16:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't realized it yet, boy,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.57,0:16:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but your kindness drew all of us together.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.25,0:16:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is why we all trust you.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.33,0:17:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I came up with our batting order and fielding positions.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.41,0:17:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've thought up a strategy too.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.58,0:17:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to tell everyone about them.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.84,0:17:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,As the leader of the Little Busters.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.84,0:17:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you could do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.53,0:17:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyousuke, I'm still weak right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.02,0:17:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I think about others, I feel like I can become stronger.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.08,0:17:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to become even stronger so that I can support everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.85,0:17:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So that, one day, I can be as good a leader as you were.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.49,0:17:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki, ever since we were kids,\Nwe shared our fun and laughter.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.42,0:17:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We've spent time together that made our hearts dance.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.70,0:17:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But every story has to come to an end.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.31,0:17:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can stay a kid forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.87,0:17:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Time passes, and people grow up.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.34,0:17:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There will come a day when we will no longer be together.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.15,0:17:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you're graduating a year before us.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.28,0:18:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And that we'll all go our separate ways some day, ending all of the fun that we've had.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.02,0:18:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you told me not to rely on you anymore, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.77,0:18:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even without me, you'll be able to keep going.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.03,0:18:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to become stronger.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.06,0:18:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I will.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.08,0:18:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The day will come when we go our separate ways.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.47,0:18:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But for now, let's play some baseball!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.27,0:18:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.43,0:18:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's enjoy the fact that the Little Busters are one.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.81,0:18:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.76,0:18:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start the game.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.74,0:18:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My balls aren't good. They'll hit them.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.70,0:18:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.49,0:18:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin, even if they hit them, we have your back.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.62,0:19:02.38,opRomaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4\be2\bord2}hitori ga tsurai kara futatsu no te wo tsunaida
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.62,0:19:02.38,opEng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4\be2\bord2}It was too hard for one to do, so two of us held hands
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:19:02.38,opRomaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}hitori ga tsurai kara futatsu no te wo tsunaida
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:19:02.38,opEng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}It was too hard for one to do, so two of us held hands
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.82,0:19:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.16,0:19:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.24,0:19:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafu!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.05,0:19:08.68,opRomaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4\be2\bord2}futari ja samishii kara wa ni natte te wo tsunaida
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.05,0:19:08.68,opEng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4\be2\bord2}But two would be too lonely, so we all came together in a circle and held hands
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:08.68,opRomaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}futari ja samishii kara wa ni natte te wo tsunaida
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:08.68,opEng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}But two would be too lonely, so we all came together in a circle and held hands
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.91,0:19:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.16,0:19:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No fear!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.25,0:19:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe in us, in your friends!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.01,0:19:16.77,opRomaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4\be2\bord2}kitto sore ga ikusen no chikara ni mo nari
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.01,0:19:16.77,opEng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4\be2\bord2}I'm sure that will be strength in itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:16.77,opRomaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}kitto sore ga ikusen no chikara ni mo nari
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:16.77,opEng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}I'm sure that will be strength in itself,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.79,0:19:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give this everything we've got!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.18,0:19:21.90,opRomaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4\be2\bord2}donna yume mo tateru ki ga surunda
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.18,0:19:21.90,opEng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4\be2\bord2}Enough to end any dream we have
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:21.90,opRomaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}donna yume mo tateru ki ga surunda
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:21.90,opEng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Enough to end any dream we have
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.05,0:19:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, it's not about winning or losing!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.80,0:19:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give them the best game we can!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.11,0:19:24.44,opRomaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4\be2\bord2}takaku tobe takaku sora he
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.11,0:19:24.44,opEng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4\be2\bord2}Fly high, high into the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:24.44,opRomaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}takaku tobe takaku sora he
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:24.44,opEng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Fly high, high into the sky,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.26,0:19:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
