Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.44,0:19:28.65,opEng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4\be2\bord2}Jump high, and raise your voice high,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:28.65,opRomaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}takaku kere takaku koe wo age
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:28.65,opEng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Jump high, and raise your voice high,
